    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >佛系鱼塘</h2><br>佛系鱼塘是一款轻松休闲的<strong>钓鱼游戏</strong>，当你做其他事情时，游戏界面会<strong>待机等你来玩</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027650/extras/iw_ch-sc_text_fishing-bottom.png?t=1749692621\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027650/extras/iw_gif_bottom.gif?t=1749692621\" /></span><br>在游戏过程中，你可以专注于其他事情，因为游戏界面将停留在屏幕底部。可以通过放大或缩小、改变排布方式或完全隐藏它。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027650/extras/iw_ch-sc_text_idle-fishing.png?t=1749692621\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027650/extras/iw_gif_fishing.gif?t=1749692621\" /></span><br>与其他游戏不同的是，鱼会等着你！当你想继续玩的时候，点击游戏即可开始钓鱼。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027650/extras/iw_ch-sc_text_explore.png?t=1749692621\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027650/extras/iw_gif_explore.gif?t=1749692621\" /></span><br>不同的生态系统中都有独特的鱼类供捕捉。",
